remarks.format: ## Remarks 將多個項目加入至堆疊中，使用 PushRange 是更有效率的機制，比使用一次的一個項目。When adding multiple items to the stack, using PushRange is a more efficient mechanism than using one item at a time. 此外，PushRange 保證，所有的項目會加入以不可分割的方式，這表示沒有其他執行緒能夠插入被推入的項目之間的項目。Additionally, PushRange guarantees that all of the elements will be added atomically, meaning that no other threads will be able to inject elements between the elements being pushed. 在較低的索引中的項目`items`陣列會推送之前在索引較高的項目。Items at lower indices in the `items` array will be pushed before items at higher indices. 如需程式碼範例，請參閱。For a code example, see .
